+## Apostille Services
+
+| Service | Price | Type | Processing |
+|---|---|---|---|
+| State Apostille | $200/doc | `state` | 3–10 business days |
+| Federal Apostille | $200/doc | `federal` | ~5 weeks (standard), ~10 days (priority) |
